'''Republika y’Uburundi''' n´igihugu kiri muri [[Afrika]] y´ubuseruko. Bukikujwe nu [[Rwanda]] m´uburaruko; [[Tanzania]] m´ubuseruko hamwe na Republika iharanira demokarasi ya kongo [[RDC]] m'uburengero. Ikiyaga [[Tanganyika]] kiri mu burengero bw'[[Uburundi]] kiri hafi y'umurwa mukuru [[Bujumbura]] kikaba ari ica kabiri kw'isi gifise musi kure cane.

== Akahise ==
Abashakashatsi bavuga y´uko Uburundi bwamyeho nk´igihugu c´ikukiye kuva mukinjana ca 16. Mu mwaka 1903 niho c´atakaza 
intahe y´ukwikukira igihe hashikiye abadagi;umwami w'ico gihe [[Mwezi Gisabo]] akaba yasinye hamwe na bo Umwumvikano w'i Kiganda "Traité de Kiganda"(mu kinyamazuru). Haheze ingwano y´isi yose ya mbere caciye kiba ubukoloni bw'igihugu c´ububiligi.
Uburundi bwafatanijwe n´igihugu cu Rwanda: [[Rwanda-urundi]]. Kuwa 1 Mukakaro 1962 niho casubira kuronka intahe yaco 
y´ukwikukira irondewe n´umuganwa [[Louis Rwagasore|Rwagasore Louis]] umuhungu w'umwami Mwambutsa Bangiricenge akaba n'umukuru w´umugambwe w'abadasigana [[UPRONA]].
Uburundi cari igihugu cifashe kandi cagutse.Munyuma ku ntwaro ya babiligi gitakaza bugufi imwe mu ntara yari nini, ica yegukira Tanzaniya.

== Ubutunzi ==
Uburundi n´igihugu gitunzwe cane cane n´uburimyi hamwe n´ubworozi. Ibice 90% vy´abarundi nico bakora. Kuva 1993 ah´ingwano itereye bifatanijwe n´ibihano bwafatiwe mu 1996 n´ibihugu bibanyi vyo kwugara imbibe; ubukene bwariyongereye cane. Ubu Uburundi buriko buratororokana kuva aho hasinyiwe amasezerano hagati yimigwi yahora igwanya ubutegetsi hamwe nigisoda ca leta. Abahinga babona ko uburundi bufise kazoza keza.

